00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:54,000
<font color="#00ff00">Father Jerome.</font>

197
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:57,040
<font color="#ffffff">What do you think should be done?</font>

198
00:20:58,360 --> 00:21:00,440
<font color="#00ff00">The author must be imprisoned</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for heresy.</font>

199
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,360
<font color="#00ffff">Father Heyst.</font>

200
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:15,400
<font color="#00ffff">There were dozens more like it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">hidden throughout the building.</font>

201
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:18,800
<font color="#00ffff">All attendees imprisoned,</font>

202
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:21,600
<font color="#00ffff">as well as anyone found in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">possession of the author's work.</font>

203
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:23,240
<font color="#ffffff">Mm-hm.</font>

204
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,920
<font color="#ffffff">Father...?</font>

205
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:33,640
<font color="#ffff00">Gomez.</font>

206
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:34,880
<font color="#ffffff">Father Gomez.</font>

207
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,720
<font color="#ffffff">If you were in my position,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">what would you do?</font>

208
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:40,840
<font color="#ffff00">Physical atonement.</font>

209
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:42,440
<font color="#ffff00">In public.</font>

210
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:47,640
<font color="#ffff00">For those charged with possession,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'd choose perhaps the whip.</font>

211
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:51,280
<font color="#ffff00">For the author, something which</font>
<font color="#ffff00">leaves a little more...</font>

212
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:54,000
<font color="#ffff00">..lasting damage.</font>

213
00:21:56,800 --> 00:22:00,480
<font color="#ffff00">Fear is a gift.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It allows people to learn.</font>

214
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,640
<font color="#00ffff">He will make examples of us.</font>

215
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:07,720
<font color="#00ffff">Baruch, we do not have time.</font>

216
00:22:09,520 --> 00:22:11,280
<font color="#00ff00">We need that knife.</font>

217
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:14,840
<font color="#ffff00">I told you to stop following me.</font>

218
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:16,960
<font color="#ffff00">How can you cut through worlds?</font>

219
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:19,840
<font color="#00ffff">We are made of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Dust and can pass through</font>

220
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:21,720
<font color="#00ffff">invisible spaces in the air,</font>

221
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:24,440
<font color="#00ffff">gateways into other worlds.</font>

222
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:26,720
<font color="#00ffff">We can see them, but you cannot.</font>

223
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:30,000
<font color="#00ff00">Balthamos and I have been</font>
<font color="#00ff00">searching for Aesahaettr,</font>

224
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:34,240
<font color="#00ff00">for you,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">because there is a great war coming.</font>

225
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:37,680
<font color="#00ff00">All conscious beings</font>
<font color="#00ff00">are engaged in a battle already,</font>

226
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:39,320
<font color="#00ff00">though not all of us know it.</font>

227
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:42,440
<font color="#00ff00">The enemy's power is</font>
<font color="#00ff00">growing stronger every minute,</font>

228
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:44,920
<font color="#00ff00">and you have the weapon</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that will enable us to win.</font>

229
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:48,680
<font color="#00ff00">You must come</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with us to Lord Asriel.</font>

230
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:51,400
<font color="#00ff00">He is gathering an army...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I know who he is.</font>

231
00:22:52,760 --> 00:22:54,840
<font color="#ffff00">Someone told me about him.</font>

232
00:22:54,840 --> 00:22:56,120
<font color="#ffff00">About all of it.</font>

233
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:57,720
<font color="#ffff00">The war.</font>

234
00:22:57,720 --> 00:23:01,080
<font color="#ffff00">How I'm supposed to fight</font>
<font color="#ffff00">alongside Asriel, with this.</font>

235
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:04,680
<font color="#ffff00">I can't go with you.</font>

236
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:08,360
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm looking for my friend Lyra.</font>

237
00:23:08,360 --> 00:23:10,000
<font color="#ffff00">Asriel's daughter.</font>

238
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:13,840
<font color="#ffff00">Not that he cares, but...</font>

239
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:16,080
<font color="#ffff00">..she's lost and she needs my help.</font>

240
00:23:16,080 --> 00:23:19,720
<font color="#00ffff">You don't understand - that knife is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">more important than you can imagine.</font>

241
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:21,000
<font color="#ffff00">No, YOU don't understand.</font>

242
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:23,640
<font color="#ffff00">Lyra's the most</font>
<font color="#ffff00">important thing to me right now.</font>

243
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:26,400
<font color="#ffff00">I'm going to find her.</font>

244
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:27,960
<font color="#00ffff">You will come with us now!</font>

245
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:30,680
<font color="#ffff00">Or what?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I'm sorry about your friend.</font>

246
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,400
<font color="#00ff00">I can see she means a lot to you.</font>

247
00:23:34,760 --> 00:23:36,640
<font color="#00ff00">Do you know what happened to her?</font>

248
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,160
<font color="#ffff00">We were attacked.</font>

249
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:39,360
<font color="#ffff00">She was taken.</font>

250
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:41,240
<font color="#00ff00">By who?</font><font color="#ffff00"> I don't know.</font>

251
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:42,680
<font color="#ffff00">I went ahead without her.</font>

252
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:44,640
<font color="#ffff00">I thought she would be safe.</font>

253
00:23:46,520 --> 00:23:48,480
<font color="#ffff00">But when I came back,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">she was gone.</font>

254
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:51,360
<font color="#ffff00">Whatever Asriel wants,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he can wait.</font>

255
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,280
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry.</font>

256
00:23:56,360 --> 00:23:59,000
<font color="#00ffff">You do realise we're just going to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">keep following you</font>

257
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:02,360
<font color="#00ffff">until you change your mind?</font><font color="#ffff00"> Well,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you can keep following me because...</font>

258
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:08,640
<font color="#ffff00">You've managed to find me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">every time I've cut through.</font>

259
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,520
<font color="#ffff00">How?</font><font color="#00ffff"> The knife.</font>

260
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:14,840
<font color="#00ffff">It attracts Dust.</font>

261
00:24:14,840 --> 00:24:17,480
<font color="#00ffff">We have senses that humans do not.</font>

262
00:24:20,520 --> 00:24:22,000
<font color="#ffff00">Help me find her.</font>

263
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:24,560
<font color="#ffff00">If you can find me,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you can find Lyra.</font>

264
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:28,600
<font color="#ffff00">Take me to her.</font>

265
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:31,000
<font color="#ffff00">Then I'll come with you to Asriel.</font>

266
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:33,440
<font color="#00ffff">We do not have time.</font>

267
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:36,520
<font color="#00ffff">It will not take them long, Baruch.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">They will find us.</font>

268
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:38,000
<font color="#00ff00">So we will be quick.</font>

269
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:41,120
<font color="#00ff00">Balthamos, we don't have a choice.</font>

270
00:24:42,120 --> 00:24:43,840
<font color="#ffff00">This was Lyra's.</font>

271
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:49,200
<font color="#ffff00">She says it's powered</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the same way as the knife.</font>

272
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:53,920
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe you can use it to find her.</font>

273
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:56,920
<font color="#00ff00">It's powered by Dust?</font>

274
00:24:58,040 --> 00:24:59,520
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, yes.</font>

275
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:03,200
<font color="#00ff00">We will need a little time,</font>

276
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:06,880
<font color="#00ff00">but we will find her,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">whatever world she is in.</font>

277
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,560
<font color="#ffffff">BUZZER</font>

278
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:35,720
<font color="#ffffff">ECHOING:</font><font color="#ffff00"> Lyra! Up here!</font>

279
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,360
<font color="#ffffff">Wait, I'm coming!</font>

280
00:25:41,280 --> 00:25:43,720
<font color="#ffffff">Roger, what is this place?</font>

281
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,480
<font color="#ffff00">I hate it!</font>

282
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:47,200
<font color="#ffffff">Roger!</font>

283
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,600
<font color="#ffffff">Roger!</font>

284
00:25:49,600 --> 00:25:51,040
<font color="#ffff00">I'm scared!</font>

285
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:52,440
<font color="#ffffff">Roger...</font>

286
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,640
<font color="#ffffff">Roger...</font>

287
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:20,080
<font color="#ffffff">Come on.</font>

288
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:34,800
<font color="#ffffff">Machi!</font>

289
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,600
<font color="#ffff00">Father!</font>

290
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:39,440
<font color="#ffffff">OGUNWE CHUCKLES</font>

291
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:44,080
<font color="#ffffff">God, I missed you. Oh, my sweet.</font>

292
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,800
<font color="#ffffff">Look at you.</font>

293
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,640
<font color="#ffffff">CHEERFUL CHATTER</font>

294
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:06,920
<font color="#ffffff">Daddy has work to do.</font>

295
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,440
<font color="#ffffff">I'll be right back.</font>

296
00:27:10,840 --> 00:27:12,360
<font color="#ffffff">SNIFFS</font>

297
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:20,840
<font color="#00ff00">You have a beautiful little girl.</font>

298
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:27,840
<font color="#00ff00">How long since you last saw her?</font>

299
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:31,920
<font color="#ffffff">Ten months and 16 days.</font>

300
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:34,360
<font color="#ffffff">I had no hope of leaving that cell</font>

301
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:37,440
<font color="#ffffff">until you and your</font>
<font color="#ffffff">cat came to recruit me.</font>

302
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,800
<font color="#00ff00">What?</font>

303
00:27:38,800 --> 00:27:42,000
<font color="#ffffff">I'm trying to decide</font>
<font color="#ffffff">if you're a madman...</font>

304
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:45,200
<font color="#ffffff">..or a genius.</font>

305
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,920
<font color="#00ff00">Well, I rather hoped</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the two could coexist.</font>

306
00:27:53,320 --> 00:27:56,280
<font color="#ffffff">So, Lord Asriel,</font>

307
00:27:56,280 --> 00:27:59,520
<font color="#ffffff">tell me who your war is really</font>
<font color="#ffffff">against and what you want from me.</font>

308
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:01,560
<font color="#00ff00">My fight is with</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Authority himself...</font>

309
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:04,600
<font color="#ffffff">You said that before,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">but it's impossible.</font>

310
00:28:06,040 --> 00:28:09,680
<font color="#ffffff">Humankind cannot</font>
<font color="#ffffff">stand against its Creator.</font>

311
00:28:09,680 --> 00:28:12,720
<font color="#00ff00">Well, he forces us to kneel at</font>
<font color="#00ff00">his feet, but he is not the Creator.</font>

312
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:14,760
<font color="#00ff00">It's all a lie.</font>

313
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:17,200
<font color="#00ff00">He's an angel.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">An angel?</font>

314
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,400
<font color="#00ff00">Nothing more.</font>

315
00:28:19,520 --> 00:28:21,160
<font color="#ffffff">And how do you know all this?</font>

316
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:24,880
<font color="#ffffff">Even if it were true.</font>

317
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:28,040
<font color="#00ff00">Some millennia ago,</font>

318
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:30,720
<font color="#00ff00">another angel discovered</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Authority's secret.</font>

319
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:34,360
<font color="#00ff00">Now that angel, Xaphania,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">sits on my council.</font>

320
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,720
<font color="#00ff00">Ogunwe,</font>

321
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:41,440
<font color="#00ff00">I am gathering the greatest</font>
<font color="#00ff00">from every world,</font>

322
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:43,160
<font color="#00ff00">from even the heavens above,</font>

323
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:46,200
<font color="#00ff00">but I want you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to help me wage my war.</font>

324
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:51,400
<font color="#ffffff">I should be flattered.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Well, I have come</font>

325
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:54,040
<font color="#00ff00">rather a long way,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">so, yes, you should.</font>

326
00:28:57,320 --> 00:28:58,920
<font color="#ffffff">Lord Asriel...</font>

327
00:29:00,280 --> 00:29:02,040
<font color="#ffffff">..I cannot help you.</font>

328
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:07,000
<font color="#ffffff">Machi is my youngest daughter.</font>

329
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:11,640
<font color="#ffffff">But I have another.</font>

330
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:23,280
<font color="#ffffff">The Temple have been targeting</font>
<font color="#ffffff">our children for a while now.</font>

331
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:31,640
<font color="#ffffff">But in recent years,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">they began taking them away...</font>

332
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,600
<font color="#ffffff">..for training.</font>

333
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,920
<font color="#ffffff">Aria...</font>

334
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:44,120
<font color="#ffffff">..is the property of the Temple.</font>

335
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:46,960
<font color="#ffffff">To her...</font>

336
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:49,960
<font color="#ffffff">..I do not exist.</font>

337
00:29:51,280 --> 00:29:53,040
<font color="#ffffff">There is only the Authority.</font>

338
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:56,200
<font color="#ffffff">And the girl I knew...</font>

339
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,520
<font color="#ffffff">..she's gone.</font>

340
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:04,800
<font color="#ffffff">But she's still my child.</font>

341
00:30:15,840 --> 00:30:17,800
<font color="#ffffff">I understand what you offer,</font>

342
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:20,480
<font color="#ffffff">but I have my</font>
<font color="#ffffff">own battles here to fight,</font>

343
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:23,640
<font color="#ffffff">and an obligation</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to save as many sons...</font>

344
00:30:25,320 --> 00:30:27,120
<font color="#ffffff">..and daughters as I can.</font>

345
00:30:27,120 --> 00:30:29,520
<font color="#00ff00">May I?</font>

346
00:30:29,520 --> 00:30:31,000
<font color="#00ff00">Please?</font>

347
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:51,320
<font color="#00ff00">I've seen this before.</font>

348
00:30:51,320 --> 00:30:54,920
<font color="#00ff00">Her daemon has been severed.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">She is not demonic!</font>

349
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:56,640
<font color="#00ff00">I did not say she was, forgive me.</font>

350
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:58,720
<font color="#00ff00">Please, if you'll</font>
<font color="#00ff00">allow me to explain.</font>

351
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:00,520
<font color="#00ff00">Stelmaria?</font>

352
00:31:03,760 --> 00:31:07,360
<font color="#00ff00">Stelmaria and I are one.</font>

353
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:10,000
<font color="#00ff00">She is my daemon.</font>

354
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:12,320
<font color="#00ff00">My soul, if you use that word.</font>

355
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:16,960
<font color="#00ff00">Aria's daemon resided within.</font>

356
00:31:18,040 --> 00:31:20,080
<font color="#00ff00">The link that</font>
<font color="#00ff00">binds us to our daemon</font>

357
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:23,120
<font color="#00ff00">is immensely powerful,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but when it is severed,</font>

358
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:25,000
<font color="#00ff00">well...</font>

359
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:26,840
<font color="#00ff00">..very little remains.</font>

360
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:31,400
<font color="#00ff00">They are taking our souls, Ogunwe,</font>

361
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:34,320
<font color="#00ff00">and with them our humanity,</font>

362
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:37,040
<font color="#00ff00">to make us easier to control.</font>

363
00:31:37,040 --> 00:31:39,000
<font color="#00ff00">To make us this.</font>

364
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:41,600
<font color="#ffffff">DISTANT HUMMING</font>

365
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:42,760
<font color="#ffffff">Drones!</font>

366
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:47,080
<font color="#ffffff">Get Machi underground!</font>

367
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:48,720
<font color="#ffffff">Everyone inside now!</font>

368
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:56,320
<font color="#00ffff">Hold your fire.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">They're trying to draw us out.</font>

369
00:31:57,800 --> 00:31:59,760
<font color="#ffffff">CLICKING</font>

370
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:29,240
<font color="#ffff00">You sent for me, Father President.</font>

371
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:31,200
<font color="#ffffff">Come in, Father Gomez.</font>

372
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,960
<font color="#ffffff">I have come to Geneva</font>

373
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:41,920
<font color="#ffffff">on a matter of great significance.</font>

374
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:47,040
<font color="#ffffff">Fra Pavel's alethiometer</font>
<font color="#ffffff">has informed me of a prophecy,</font>

375
00:32:47,040 --> 00:32:49,040
<font color="#ffffff">which, if true,</font>

376
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:51,360
<font color="#ffffff">and I believe it is,</font>

377
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:54,320
<font color="#ffffff">risks plunging us into a darkness</font>

378
00:32:54,320 --> 00:32:58,080
<font color="#ffffff">the like of which</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the world has not experienced.</font>

379
00:32:59,160 --> 00:33:03,360
<font color="#ffffff">There is a girl wandering the earth</font>
<font color="#ffffff">at this very moment,</font>

380
00:33:03,360 --> 00:33:06,560
<font color="#ffffff">and she is Eve,</font>

381
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:08,520
<font color="#ffffff">the mother of us all.</font>

382
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:10,080
<font color="#ffffff">And, of course, of all sin.</font>

383
00:33:10,080 --> 00:33:15,080
<font color="#ffffff">The instrument says that if this</font>
<font color="#ffffff">child is tempted by the serpent,</font>

384
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:19,000
<font color="#ffffff">she will likely fall. And if she</font>
<font color="#ffffff">does fall, then sin...</font>

385
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:23,680
<font color="#ffffff">..and Dust will triumph.</font>

386
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,400
<font color="#ffffff">This cannot happen.</font>

